export default { heading:'SQUARED AWAY', main:`

    Need help with Education Benefits?

    Veterans both new to their career and retired are in need of resources to help them thrive in the civilian world. At Squared Away we do our very best to provide easy access to those resources through research and dedication to serving those who fight for our freedom.

    Interested in Volunteering?

    Squared Away can connect you with various veteran support organizations. So that you can give back to our country's veterans by training service dogs, building houses for the homeless, or assisting a vet to their VA appointments. You may even want to give one-on-one mentorship to veterans reentering the civilian workforce by participating in mock interviews or resume editing sessions.

    Build your Resume here.

    Square Away allows our users to build a Resume free of charge. Once your resume is complete feel free to download for personal use, or upload it to your profile with any of the various job seeking organizations. (e.g. LinkedIn, Monster, or Glassdoor.)
